Something's off...

95
00:06:58,520 --> 00:07:00,260
<i>H-Huh?</i>

96
00:07:00,670 --> 00:07:03,270
<i>What were my lines again?</i>

97
00:07:04,310 --> 00:07:06,290
What's wrong, Shiraki?!

98
00:07:06,290 --> 00:07:07,330
Pull yourself together!

99
00:07:07,330 --> 00:07:09,030
Do you want to ruin everything?!

100
00:07:09,410 --> 00:07:14,130
<i>I can't get a single line out, 
let alone support President...</i>

101
00:07:14,130 --> 00:07:16,510
<i>I'm basically just dragging her down...</i>

102
00:07:18,820 --> 00:07:21,000
<i>I knew I couldn't handle...</i>

103
00:07:21,370 --> 00:07:22,960
