<i>What?!</i>

105
00:07:43,310 --> 00:07:46,150
Next, get the set for the ball ready!

106
00:07:46,150 --> 00:07:48,190
Hurry with her dress change!

107
00:07:48,190 --> 00:07:49,210
Got it!

108
00:07:51,110 --> 00:07:53,950
<i>So she brought us back to right 
before the ball scene.</i>

109
00:07:53,950 --> 00:07:57,210
