a little bit of time?

110
00:07:57,210 --> 00:07:58,160
Got it!

111
00:07:58,430 --> 00:08:00,590
Shirota-kun, may I have a word?

112
00:08:00,590 --> 00:08:01,800
S-Sure!

113
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:05,050
What was that complete mess-up just now?!

114
00:08:06,410 --> 00:08:08,960
Are you trying to ruin my play?

115
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:10,810
<i>I knew she'd be angry!</i>

116
00:08:10,810 --> 00:08:12,560
I-I'm sorry...

117
00:08:12,930 --> 00:08:16,210
Listen. I'll give you a piece of advice.

118
00:08:16,210 --> 00:08:17,140
Okay...

119
00:08:17,550 --> 00:08:21,310
