will draw more attention than you.

123
00:08:29,980 --> 00:08:32,840
<i>What's the meaning of "advice" again?</i>

124
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:37,930
In fact, if you have the energy 
to pay attention to others instead of me,

125
00:08:37,930 --> 00:08:39,910
