Thank you, I'll be right there.

129
00:08:48,380 --> 00:08:49,740
Basically,

130
00:08:49,740 --> 00:08:53,840
nobody ever expects 
anything from you whatsoever.

131
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:03,050
Don't waste time being intimidated. 
Don't pay attention to others.

132
00:09:03,690 --> 00:09:05,440
Just keep your eyes on me.

133
00:09:07,500 --> 00:09:08,610
Oh!

134
00:09:08,610 --> 00:09:11,320
What a beautiful young lady.

135
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:14,900
You must hail from a distinguished house!

136
00:09:15,870 --> 00:09:17,860
Prince, time to go!

137
00:09:18,890 --> 00:09:22,830
<i>As always, her words were full of thorns.</i>

138
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:24,460
<i>But still,</i>

139
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:31,200
<i>the kindness that is always wrapped 
inside them put me at ease.</i>

140
00:09:34,590 --> 00:09:36,310
<i>And more than anything...</i>

141
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:44,190
Beautiful lady, would you honor me 
by allowing me to have this dance?

142
00:09:44,770 --> 00:09:48,940
<i>I now believe that those words 
came so easily then...</i>

143
00:09:54,420 --> 00:09:55,600
With pleasure.

144
00:09:56,890 --> 00:09:59,470
<i>because it wasn't acting.</i>

145
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:02,120
<i>That's the way I see it now.</i>

146
00:10:02,950 --> 00:10:07,960
<i></i><i>Please Put Them On,</i>

147
00:10:02,950 --> 00:10:07,960
<i>Takamine-san</i>

148
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:12,960
<i></i><i>Please Put Them On,</i>

149
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:12,960
<i></i><i>Takamine-san</i>

150
00:10:13,690 --> 00:10:18,230
Beautiful lady, would you honor me 
by allowing me to have this dance?

151
00:10:23,100 --> 00:10:24,310
With pleasure.

152
00:10:25,250 --> 00:10:26,510
<i>I said it!</i>

153
00:10:26,510 --> 00:10:31,010
<i>I managed to make it through 
the first scene, thanks to her pep talk.</i>

154
00:10:31,010 --> 00:10:33,570
<i>Um, so, after this...</i>

155
00:10:35,830 --> 00:10:39,400
<i>After cutting the lights, 
there will be a spotlight on President.</i>

156
00:10:39,790 --> 00:10:41,500
<i>She will have her solo.</i>

157
00:10:41,500 --> 00:10:43,700
<i>Then the lights will be cut again,</i>

158
00:10:44,540 --> 00:10:48,210
<i>and we'll be in the dance scene.</i>

159
00:10:48,210 --> 00:10:49,850
<i>Did I get that right?</i>

160
00:10:49,850 --> 00:10:52,560
<i>So I just wait here until the lights come on.</i>

161
00:10:55,380 --> 00:10:57,840
<i>A-A-A butt!</i>

162
00:10:57,840 --> 00:11:01,180
<i>And this cloth around me... it can't be...</i>

163
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:04,640
<i>I'm inside her skirt?!</i>

164
00:11:05,780 --> 00:11:08,600
<i>Is she telling me to 
put panties on her right now?!</i>

165
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:12,020
<i>But I didn't bring any underwear for her!</i>

166
00:11:12,560 --> 00:11:15,130
Yes, it's true,

167
00:11:15,130 --> 00:11:17,850
I don't wish for many things.

168
00:11:17,850 --> 00:11:23,140
I don't wish for grandiose things.

169
00:11:23,530 --> 00:11:28,620
I just have this scant hope,

170
00:11:27,190 --> 00:11:28,620
<i>In my pocket?</i>

171
00:11:28,620 --> 00:11:34,610
a small handful in my pocket.

172
00:11:33,170 --> 00:11:35,000
<i>A scant hope?!</i>

173
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:39,710
So please, oh bells...

174
00:11:35,570 --> 00:11:39,470
<i>I mean, having no underwear 
on stage is seriously too risky...</i>

175
00:11:40,050 --> 00:11:48,270
Just for tonight, hold your breath.

176
00:11:49,450 --> 00:11:52,220
<i>I need to finishing putting these on 
during her solo...</i>

177
00:11:52,690 --> 00:11:55,420
<i>before the stage is lit up again!</i>

178
00:11:56,230 --> 00:12:01,190
Oh my beloved person.

179
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:02,510
<i>Wait!</i>

180
00:12:01,670 --> 00:12:07,230
Please only look at me.

181
00:12:02,950 --> 00:12:04,450
<i>Please don't move!</i>

182
00:12:07,230 --> 00:12:17,670
Hold me tight and take me 
to a world of our own.

183
00:12:18,150 --> 00:12:20,590
But you know?

184
00:12:20,590 --> 00:12:23,820
I am aware.

185
00:12:23,820 --> 00:12:29,350
This dream is already over.

186
00:12:29,620 --> 00:12:35,850
So please don't ever peek

187
00:12:35,850 --> 00:12:41,900
at these hidden feelings.

188
00:12:54,210 --> 00:12:57,940
Now, everyone, let's dance 
to our hearts' content!

189
00:12:57,940 --> 00:13:00,550
Let's make this an unforgettable night.

190
00:13:01,050 --> 00:13:03,130
<i>I-I made it!</i>

191
00:13:05,060 --> 00:13:07,640
<i>After that, I followed her lead.</i>

192
00:13:08,030 --> 00:13:09,140
Please wait!

193
00:13:09,850 --> 00:13:12,470
Please, please don't follow me!

194
00:13:12,790 --> 00:13:18,130
<i>And the crazy act of putting panties on her 
on stage had blown away my nervousness,</i>

195
00:13:18,130 --> 00:13:20,750
<i>so I was able to continue on without incident.</i>

196
00:13:21,970 --> 00:13:24,700
<i>And then we finally got to the climax.</i>

197
00:13:25,400 --> 00:13:30,740
Th-This is Cinderella, a lowly girl 
not any better than a servant...

198
00:13:30,740 --> 00:13:33,120
There is no way that 
she's the person of your heart.

199
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:35,080
Her standing is of no consequence to me.

200
00:13:35,510 --> 00:13:39,440
The person whose foot fits 
this slipper is the person of my heart.

201
00:13:40,590 --> 00:13:44,620
Cinderella, would you allow me 
to put it on you?

202
00:13:45,270 --> 00:13:48,170
Huh? Did someone take the spare costume?

203
00:13:48,170 --> 00:13:49,970
Oh, yeah, just now—

204
00:13:51,110 --> 00:13:55,930
I bet nobody even suspects this is the second 
time you've put something on my body on stage.

205
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:57,860
H-Hey!

206
00:13:58,920 --> 00:14:00,100
Quiet!

207
00:14:01,610 --> 00:14:03,940
Stop!

208
00:14:04,260 --> 00:14:06,780
That Prince is an impostor!

209
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:07,990
Huh?!

210
00:14:07,990 --> 00:14:13,580
He is a commoner who tried to take 
my place while I was away due to an injury!

211
00:14:13,900 --> 00:14:16,480
Even his face screams "commoner!"

212
00:14:16,960 --> 00:14:18,410
What?!

213
00:14:18,410 --> 00:14:20,940
Kou-chan is way cooler!

214
00:14:20,940 --> 00:14:22,200
He's so unassuming!

215
00:14:22,200 --> 00:14:24,920
They put a real twist in the story.

216
00:14:25,220 --> 00:14:27,220
<i>What is happening?</i>

217
00:14:27,220 --> 00:14:29,460
<i>This wasn't in the script, was it?!</i>

218
00:14:30,390 --> 00:14:32,140
<i></i><i>Ouji's become unhinged!</i>

219
00:14:32,010 --> 00:14:34,470
<i></i><i>Please play along
 and improvise!!</i>

220
00:14:32,530 --> 00:14:34,470
<i>What now?!</i>

221
00:14:34,470 --> 00:14:36,780
T-Two princes?!

222
00:14:36,780 --> 00:14:37,770
What is happening?!

223
00:14:37,770 --> 00:14:39,060
<i>She's so quick!</i>

224
00:14:39,380 --> 00:14:40,610
Cinderella!

225
00:14:40,610 --> 00:14:44,270
You mustn't allow such 
an uncouth man touch you!

226
00:14:44,270 --> 00:14:45,680
<i>Uncouth?!</i>

227
00:14:45,680 --> 00:14:48,900
Behold his filthy hands!

228
00:14:49,280 --> 00:14:53,890
In contrast, I have been applying hand cream 
and polishing my nails for a week,

229
00:14:53,890 --> 00:14:55,410
all for this one day!

230
00:14:56,070 --> 00:15:00,670
I am fully prepared to touch your lovely feet!

231
00:15:01,580 --> 00:15:03,790
<i>Are you telling me...</i>

232
00:15:04,130 --> 00:15:08,110
<i>That Ouji flipped out because he
wants to touch her foot?!</i>

233
00:15:08,110 --> 00:15:13,090
Cinderella's... beautiful... feet!

234
00:15:14,800 --> 00:15:16,680
<i>Are you really about to destroy the last fun</i>

235
00:15:16,680 --> 00:15:19,490
<i>high school cultural festival that 
President has been working for?</i>

236
00:15:19,490 --> 00:15:22,590
<i>For your own selfish wants?!</i>

237
00:15:25,620 --> 00:15:28,940
Oh, please don't fight.

238
00:15:28,940 --> 00:15:31,980
If you truly do love me...

239
00:15:31,980 --> 00:15:33,000
I won't give her up.

240
00:15:34,190 --> 00:15:36,940
Even if you were the real Prince

241
00:15:36,940 --> 00:15:39,110
and I was a commoner.

242
00:15:39,580 --> 00:15:43,180
Someone who is selfish and won't 
consider what she wants

243
00:15:43,710 --> 00:15:46,880
won't be able to make her happy.

244
00:15:49,900 --> 00:15:51,530
I will not let you have her!

245
00:15:51,990 --> 00:15:53,800
I will make her happy!

246
00:16:02,440 --> 00:16:05,400
Only Kou-chan wins!!

247
00:16:02,440 --> 00:16:05,400
Wow, Kou-chan is so cool!

248
00:16:05,400 --> 00:16:08,230
Knock it off. You're so embarrassing.

249
00:16:08,510 --> 00:16:11,070
I don't know what's going on, but it's good!

250
00:16:11,070 --> 00:16:12,620
Give it some fitting narration!

251
00:16:12,620 --> 00:16:13,240
Got it!

252
00:16:13,240 --> 00:16:16,090
The real Prince, who appeared out of nowhere,

253
00:16:16,090 --> 00:16:19,700
and the impostor Prince, who's 
ready to face off with him!

254
00:16:20,040 --> 00:16:22,870
Who is Cinderella going to choo—

255
00:16:37,540 --> 00:16:39,640
P-Pre—

256
00:16:40,090 --> 00:16:42,100
Let us go.

257
00:16:42,100 --> 00:16:45,240
Y-Yes. Where to?!

258
00:16:46,060 --> 00:16:48,940
Please wait, Pres— Cinderella!

259
00:16:49,620 --> 00:16:50,940
What about the slipper?!

260
00:16:57,130 --> 00:16:58,720
You may have it.

261
00:17:03,200 --> 00:17:05,920
Neither slipper nor standing matter!

262
00:17:05,920 --> 00:17:10,440
Cinderella has found true love!

263
00:17:16,410 --> 00:17:18,860
<i>After that, the play went smoothly.</i>

264
00:17:18,860 --> 00:17:22,170
<i>Ironically, the fresh twist 
in the second half was well-received,</i>

265
00:17:22,170 --> 00:17:24,100
<i>and our show was a huge success.</i>

266
00:17:24,100 --> 00:17:26,920
You gotta do that wild entrance 
in the afternoon showing too.

267
00:17:26,920 --> 00:17:29,310
Huh? Uh, sure...

268
00:17:29,310 --> 00:17:30,970
<i>But even more than that,</i>

269
00:17:30,970 --> 00:17:33,740
<i>what had impressed 
our classmates even more was...</i>

270
00:17:33,740 --> 00:17:35,760
B-By the way, President...

271
00:17:36,280 --> 00:17:37,840
The thing at the end...

272
00:17:37,840 --> 00:17:39,990
Did you really kiss?!

273
00:17:41,160 --> 00:17:45,530
It was just something I did to salvage 
that situation, so it wasn't real.

274
00:17:45,530 --> 00:17:48,960
But it's embarrassing, so please 
don't talk about it too much.

275
00:17:49,420 --> 00:17:51,420
Right, Shirota-kun?

276
00:17:51,420 --> 00:17:53,380
R-Right...

277
00:18:03,310 --> 00:18:05,270
Fujihigashi Festival

278
00:18:11,400 --> 00:18:13,360
<i></i><i>Fu</i><i>ji</i><i>hi</i><i>ga</i><i>shi </i><i>Fe</i><i>sti</i><i>val</i>

279
00:18:13,750 --> 00:18:16,930
I'm glad the cultural festival went well.

280
00:18:16,930 --> 00:18:18,430
Me too.

281
00:18:18,430 --> 00:18:21,070
I'm glad our play was a big success as well.

282
00:18:21,070 --> 00:18:24,080
That was because of my godly improvisation.

283
00:18:25,990 --> 00:18:29,510
Your acting also gets passing marks,

284
00:18:32,090 --> 00:18:34,090
so it makes for a good memory, doesn't it?

285
00:18:36,200 --> 00:18:38,260
<i>But thinking about it...</i>

286
00:18:38,260 --> 00:18:41,400
<i>What was the meaning of that, really?</i>

287
00:18:41,400 --> 00:18:44,890
<i>I feel like it was a bit much 
for salvaging the situation...</i>

288
00:18:47,160 --> 00:18:50,580
<i>Maybe it's something like a reward,</i>

289
00:18:50,580 --> 00:18:52,870
<i>an early payment for being her closet?</i>

290
00:18:53,320 --> 00:18:55,770
<i>She's really not that kind of person, though...</i>

291
00:18:56,110 --> 00:18:57,180
<i>But...</i>

292
00:18:59,030 --> 00:19:00,410
What is it?

293
00:19:00,410 --> 00:19:02,860
It's just... that...

294
00:19:03,240 --> 00:19:05,820
That thing you did during Cinderella...

295
00:19:05,820 --> 00:19:06,700
That thing?

296
00:19:06,700 --> 00:19:10,100
W-When you... and I...

297
00:19:13,230 --> 00:19:15,610
Why do you think I did that?

298
00:19:16,970 --> 00:19:21,050
Try to think about why I did that to you.

299
00:19:22,440 --> 00:19:23,460
<i>C-Could it be?</i>

300
00:19:23,940 --> 00:19:27,030
<i>No, that's not possible... but...</i>

301
00:19:28,180 --> 00:19:29,730
If you don't get it,

302
00:19:30,140 --> 00:19:33,850
do you need me to do it again 
and again until you do?

303
00:19:41,210 --> 00:19:42,770
Ow!

304
00:19:42,770 --> 00:19:45,870
And? Did that wake up your brain?

305
00:19:45,870 --> 00:19:48,170
Do you get it now?

306
00:19:48,170 --> 00:19:49,810
If it didn't, I can do it again.

307
00:19:49,810 --> 00:19:51,410
No, it's fine!

308
00:19:51,410 --> 00:19:53,290
Then please give me your answer.

309
00:19:54,310 --> 00:19:56,990
If you don't give me the right answer...

310
00:19:56,990 --> 00:20:00,010
maybe I'll make it so that 
the play didn't go well.

311
00:20:00,500 --> 00:20:03,720
Because you couldn't get 
a single line out, or something.

312
00:20:04,800 --> 00:20:06,300
I'm joking.

313
00:20:06,700 --> 00:20:10,520
I just want to hear your honest thoughts.

314
00:20:10,520 --> 00:20:14,730
Th-This is just a theory...

315
00:20:16,230 --> 00:20:19,210
Maybe you want me...

316
00:20:20,650 --> 00:20:23,800
to keep being your closet 
at university too,

317
00:20:23,800 --> 00:20:26,220
so it was some sort of reward or something?

318
00:20:31,080 --> 00:20:32,790
<i>That was wrong?!</i>

319
00:21:19,500 --> 00:21:21,420
<i></i><i>Fu</i><i>ji</i><i>hi</i><i>ga</i><i>shi </i><i>Fe</i><i>sti</i><i>val</i>

320
00:21:24,810 --> 00:21:26,250
<i>We're back here?</i>

321
00:21:28,770 --> 00:21:30,100
<i>Is she angry?</i>

322
00:21:30,100 --> 00:21:32,200
<i>What is the right answer then?!</i>

323
00:21:34,230 --> 00:21:36,690
Why don't you think about it harder?

324
00:21:36,690 --> 00:21:38,020
About what that meant.

325
00:21:38,020 --> 00:21:39,720
Think harder?

326
00:21:39,720 --> 00:21:41,110
<i>What did it mean?</i>

327
00:21:41,790 --> 00:21:44,770
Do you need another jolt?

328
00:21:44,770 --> 00:21:47,070
Um, that's—

329
00:21:50,280 --> 00:21:52,240
<i></i><i>Fu</i><i>ji</i><i>hi</i><i>ga</i><i>shi </i><i>Fe</i><i>sti</i><i>val</i>

330
00:21:53,130 --> 00:21:54,890
Looks like time's up.

331
00:21:54,890 --> 00:21:56,460
Par for the course for Dull-ta-kun.

332
00:21:56,800 --> 00:21:59,340
Looks like it's the climax 
of the closing event.

333
00:21:59,340 --> 00:22:01,980
As the student council president, 
I need to be there.

334
00:22:01,980 --> 00:22:04,430
Um, President, I—

335
00:22:04,430 --> 00:22:07,760
You'll have to continue as my closet 
until you figure out the answer.

336
00:22:13,830 --> 00:22:17,510
<i>Quite some time will pass before I figure out</i>

337
00:22:18,920 --> 00:22:20,800
<i>what the right answer was.</i>

338
00:22:24,780 --> 00:22:25,920
Shirota-kun.

339
00:22:26,680 --> 00:22:28,830
Aren't you forgetting something?

340
00:22:35,580 --> 00:22:36,840
<i>At that point,</i>

341
00:22:38,340 --> 00:22:45,660
<i>I was simply hoping the 
relationship we had would go on.</i>

342
00:22:52,300 --> 00:22:55,480
Shall we go, then,

343
00:22:57,930 --> 00:22:59,200
Kurota-kun?

